Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考试各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}考试休息日是指高中在考试成绩发表到结业典礼之间的假期。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始到结业典礼前的三天是考试休息日  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以学校放假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去怎么打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气好的话就出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去之前说过的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要提醒大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试休息日是为了复习而准备的重要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以四处去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去的时候请大家要找个好的借口再出门哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月15日  『随感而发』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在闹钟响之前就醒来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点早  既然这么舒服干脆就起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小荠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  还没有作好出门的准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去换衣服啦  要出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个大晴天可真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去什么地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐  为什么没有告诉她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你会去说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得知道下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  去了你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:03:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻野原美术馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就想考试结束后来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到考试成绩  我就变成这种感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  罗丹的思想者雕像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答正确
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  则是非礼勿看猴  非礼勿说猴和非礼勿听猴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原意为不看不说不听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指逃避现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里由乃的脸是冈本太郎的著名雕塑建筑「太陽の塔」\N建于1970年的大阪世博会。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…乃…同…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是指…「爆发吧」的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  从这里开始参观行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面好像有露天展览呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好惬意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像来郊游一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天是考试休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能太随意  得打起精神好好学点东西再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够空手而来真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  学习…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把钱包也寄存在你那了  不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哦  我不背包的话就会不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  由乃学姐的也寄存了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很high的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快乐的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也能感觉到它的主题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲由乃亲  我们也来跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…这…这是在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下还有这样两人组合雕像的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐和寻学姐就来模仿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个…做…做不来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个雕像的标题是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「白色觉醒」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现代艺术兮兮的东西也有这样很难理解的作品在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小荠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠你觉得那座雕像的标题是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「骨折」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座雕像的标题是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次大家一起来猜猜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫「耸立」之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「树干」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「从宇宙来的问候」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「自然界的无机物」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「光溜溜」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反射成像的世界」这名怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}金属原料的圆柱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定采用乃莉的标题  大家意向如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一座露天雕塑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的话也许我也能做得出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去室内展馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然美术科的学生就会这样想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果是自己的话会做出什么样的东西来呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  果然还是会有一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话好想做一个能窥视天空的类似万花筒一样的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是不错呢  够罗曼蒂克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说做一个以「格列佛饭」为标题的  巨大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等看完全部展览吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷气好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一进到馆内  氛围就完全不同了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  变成美术馆特有的氛围了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喜欢这种稍微有些庄重的气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像连国家都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  既然同样是在这个美术世界里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许从我们高中里也会出现这样流芳百世的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说得像是人家的事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英也有那样的可能性的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是吗  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻…也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢    
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也有这种可能性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我怎么觉得人都避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可能感受到了些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  大家最喜欢的是哪幅作品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要排出顺序可不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立体的  平面的  各种各样的种类都有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  回到家后好想创作点什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:09:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  现在有种「什么都好  就是好想做做看」的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算看了这么多  虽然觉得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同时还觉得这是离我好远的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是小荠做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用筷子的包装纸做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是作品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术就在我们身边存在着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荠老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  这个已经吃完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作品标题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「思春期」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随口说说～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要表达不安感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思啊  雕刻野原美术馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能对吉野屋老师说「过了个有意义的考试休息日」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起去真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题  「把明天的我变得干干净净的东西们」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  也得把你放进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像觉得还是有些不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,署名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月15日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月28日  『轻飘飘』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好沙英  今天还真热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的学习会是11点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像到目的地之前就会融化掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是室内游泳池  里面很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家热情高涨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心  晚上再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面全部都戴进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  全都进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫不戴泳镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柜子的钥匙戴好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳镜没有忘记带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哨子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像是游泳比赛的练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  虽然小宫是要练习  我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跟着乃莉来游泳池呢  我不是很擅长游泳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠不打算出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也不擅长游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一季SP1的捏他，请自行查阅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说是浮不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想做个人练习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为这种学校泳衣会不显身材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠  你的底裤是不是露出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  人还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能练得成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条水道是给想游泳的人准备的  所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子学姐有来过这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去年和由乃亲一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…来过！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  给你漂浮板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  拿了两个来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫也要用这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试试久违的冲浪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  要站在那个上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了  失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  由乃亲浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  但是你浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃没有意识都能浮起来呢  真有天分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意识的话谁都能浮起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  关键就是因为太过用力才浮不起来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用力  不要用力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算用力也能浮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得下巴好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去那边游了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  加油练习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想试试看啊  快速转身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:24.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里是捏花王发售的扫除套装「クイックル」系列。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是变成打扫用具的样子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来进行10分钟的设备检查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请从泳池里上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  我趁现在去趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  我觉得小荠会全部脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  再努把力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阶梯状？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能陪我练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然离暑假结束没多少时间了  我知道会很勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少为了大赛好好练习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油成为班级代表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得好像有捞棋子比赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}比谁沉得快？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉你去那边练习就好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那就一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我追不上你的速度的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在这边也行  我已经游了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来玩点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乃莉聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个等回到暖阳庄再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  我觉得我刚才好像找到诀窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得一下子就哗地一下轻飘飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想一个人试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘  轻飘飘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}轻飘飘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起来了  刚才浮起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  由乃学姐  手和脚没办法伸直吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先试着划动手脚向前游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蝉鸣声  夏天也已经结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再热一段时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要来开个惯例的睡衣派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等下就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  这是最后的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  由乃  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了  我们马上就换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  欢迎大家来到睡衣派对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠的睡衣真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都在同一个屋檐下睡着  应该没有那么多新鲜感了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的派对经常开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么特别的目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家一起热热闹闹地一起睡很开心的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  大家有好好练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  结果大家一直游到傍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然中间也有休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  大概游了8公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样游的话都可以渡海了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然只是在那里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了的温水游泳池的温度感觉很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  由乃的成果怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很大的进步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃从铁锤进化成木槌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘…的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐今天第一次浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后困得要倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为非常努力才累成这样子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  作为派对的提议者却最先睡着这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议者是由乃学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为她说还没有试过大家一起睡  一直很想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着和大家一起玩  还准备了素描本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么剩下的成员来开个涂鸦大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都画不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  关于主题我来说个提议好吗
